{"tid":1277703,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例：佔領立會後首個交易日　恒指全日升332點","createTime":"2019-07-02T09:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T09:18:39.000Z","uid":134997,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"595cddba5fea7fabb9a46f4f3ee80a2850c5702b","tid":1277703,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:00:10.000Z","msg":"立法會昨日(1日)遭示威者佔據破壞，港股表現未知會否受事件影響。不過，中美貿易戰緩和，並已重開新一輪貿易談判，港股7月開局做好，恒生指數今早高開361點後一度衝上28,959點，最多升416點，全日上揚332點或1.17%，報28,875點，未能突破二萬九關。國企指數日中曾升穿一萬一關，收市漲99點或0.91%，報10,981點。主板成交錄1,123億港元。 <br />\n<br />\n美國解除華為部分限制，其中手機設備股急漲，舜宇光學科技抽升逾9%，為表現最佳藍籌；瑞聲科技漲逾7%。 <br />\n<br />\n證券分析員譚朗蔚表示，中美兩國元首在二十國集團(G20)峰會會面之結果並沒有太大驚喜，只不過是兩國暫時沒有將關稅升級，直言港股現水平不吸引，維持恒生指數於29,000點見頂的預測。他又認為，現時除手機設備股能炒上之外，內地開設科創板及人民幣匯價反彈利好A股，券商股亦有望跑贏大市。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190702/mobile/bkn-20190702092905556-0702_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190702%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190702092905556-0702_00822_001.html&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FMEwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=6181c742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190702/mobile/bkn-20190702092905556-0702_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79aba632bfa81eeb95040ddcb1eb2ce9d2361409","tid":1277703,"uid":85774,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"佔領立會 = 升<br />\n逃犯條例過 = 跌"},{"pid":"df3d600c3c13e51c6d5431957ed383ba48747b8f","tid":1277703,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7e249acf09c190447c1bed2ec598e1e3d93229","tid":1277703,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中"},{"pid":"9c7b84a1bbdf79b57e45b4fdb83231fdf63eaca8","tid":1277703,"uid":73956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"東網識玩"},{"pid":"b0877dfee779a4ba54dbf15f9c3e7600ad163c89","tid":1277703,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}